{"tid":152062,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"揀套動畫做文本分析","createTime":"2017-03-11T12:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T00:52:37.000Z","uid":86488,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"356166b796f84bbbf403f7afb15f11df1b4c5856","tid":152062,"uid":86488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:11:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟呢個禮拜有份功課<br />\n係要做有關一套動畫嘅文本分析<br />\n指出佢帶出嘅訊息同埋做批判<br />\n我想搵個容易做批判嘅題材<br />\n而家我心目中有兩套候選<br />\n小圓（成篇／抽一個故事）<br />\n怪化貓（無面男篇）<br />\n如果大家有更加好嘅意見不妨提出<br />\n最好係喺上面嗰兩套or以下幾套揀（最好比埋套嘢嘅訊息）：<br />\n死亡遊行<br />\n奇諾之旅<br />\n荒川爆笑團<br />\n高達00<br />\n心連情結<br />\n我係想要套主旨明確既動畫<br />\n唔係要啲深到睇唔明噏乜嘅"},{"pid":"6fe42f89d1ac4cb411a8792fee4b95b680c44567","tid":152062,"uid":9305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:12:57.000Z","msg":"留名等人推介魔法戰爭"},{"pid":"71c1d49b3844ecb59ec44e50a57f3da5c663f48f","tid":152062,"uid":30085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:13:43.000Z","msg":"迷家<br />\nA/Z"},{"pid":"3eb2cefec96a2245e2368a7d724cd3fcd4fd2cfd","tid":152062,"uid":86488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:17:10.000Z","msg":"利申<br />\n連登神作（魔法戰爭、迷家、glasslip）<br />\n一集都冇睇過<br />\n而家冇時間睇<br />\n功課1個禮拜後交"},{"pid":"e81240e4ceb0e057349830d0c0908c1bf52e1ffe","tid":152062,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:17:25.000Z","msg":"企鵝罐<br />\n火之鳥<br />\n三眼神童<br />\n阿童木/pluto（阿童木地上最大機械人篇）<br />\n二十世紀少年<br />\nMonster"},{"pid":"fb43a1bef8953992320ecfbd5146e20c66015878","tid":152062,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:17:53.000Z","msg":"寫完怪化貓post上黎順便屌鳩d冷番撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e560e4d2d3d7b62f56c6706ca300815b893e5b","tid":152062,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:18:51.000Z","msg":"少女與戰車 進行過份解讀將佢主題講到做女權又得"},{"pid":"0e83597b7a1c85de2600a1b304cfeb84f8a53f13","tid"